      "path": "README.md",
      "content": "# Project Structure

This project is structured as follows:

- `src/app.js`: Main application file.
- `src/server.js`: Server startup logic.
- `src/modules/projects/routes.js` and `service.js`: Routes and service for projects.
- `src/modules/tasks/routes.js` and `service.js`: Routes and service for tasks.
- `src/modules/members/routes.js` and `service.js`: Routes and service for members.
- `src/modules/comments/routes.js` and `service.js`: Routes and service for comments.
- `src/lib/errors.js`: Error handling utility.
- `src/lib/id.js`: ID generation utility."
